cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SE

The paper discusses a time synchronization attack on wide area monitoring systems in smart grid and proposes a cross layer detection mechanism to combat it. This involves techniques related to cybersecurity (cs.CR), system control (cs.SY), networking and communication (cs.NI), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and software engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.NI, cs.AI, and cs.SE, in that order.
